Text.string: The backwater hillbillies of this dinosaur-infested swamp need burgers, too! Help me make these deliveries! Go on! Do it!
And if you take out my competitor's signs, I'll cut you some slack on the time! That all rhymed!
Any time you're in the area and need work, come talk to my sign spinner. These swamp folk can't get enough of my burgers! Yeah!
Back for more burger-slingin'?! Hell yes! Get to it, delivery driver!
Ooh, ready for some more ACTION-packed burger delivery? Hnnnh, ACTION?! Of course you are! Get to it!
Ah, I see you've returned to deliver MORE FREAKIN' BURGERS! I love it! Get going!
Don't forget to take down my competitor's signs for bonus time!
Be sure to totally wreck Legacy Drive-Thru's signs for me if you want some bonus time!
And remember: shoot those Legacy signs for bonus time!
Holy HELL! That was fast! You are FREAKIN' AMAZING, my dude! Extra big payment for you this time!
Hey, pretty solid performance there, my dude!
I mean... that wasn't the WORST delivery driving I've ever seen.
Head back to my sign spinner for payment!
Please don't talk to the sign spinner. They're not paid to talk. But you! You did good, my dude! Real good! Come back for another go any time!
The sign spinner won't speak to you. That's dedication to your craft right there. Anyway, thanks, my dude! Come back for more delivery driving anytime! Folks are always hungry!
Don't worry about the silent sign spinner. They're always like that, haha! Anyway, thanks for taking care of those deliveries, my dude! Come back and do it again some time!
Legacy Drive-Thru can eat a butt!
Woo! Taking down the competition!
Great shot! Take that, sign!
Yeah! Take down the competition!
That's some bonus time for ya!
Yes! Screw that sign in particular! Hnngh!
You've gotta be the fastest delivery driver I've ever seen! Even the swamp couldn't slow you down! Extra big payment for ya!
Glad you managed to outrun all the scary monsters and get those burgers delivered! The people of Eden-6 thank you, I'm sure! And I thank you, too. Like this: THANKS!
Burgers for swamp folk!
Burger delivery! Hell yeah!
Oh, how I envy that customer and their sweet, juicy, burger-y future!
FRIGGIN' BURGERS! WOO!
Nice one! You know, we really got a good thing going here, my dude! Haha!
Yes! YES! Keep slingin' those burgers!
Your time is running out! Hurry!
Hurry it up, my dude!
Time's a-wastin'! Get moving!
Come on, come on! Do it faster!
Time's running out, but you gotta keep going!
Speed it up, slowpoke!
I don't blame you for going a little slow there. It was probably the swamp's fault, right? It wasn't you! Definitely not. Anyway, thanks!
Go back to my sign spinner and I'll have 'em pay what I owe! Come on!
